casebody.data:
STATE EX REL. STUART
v.
GREENE 2019-0592 Supreme Court of Ohio. July 24, 2019

CASE ANNOUNCEMENT

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULING

On relator's motion to submit documents in camera. Motion granted. Respondent shall submit unredacted versions of the documents requested by relator in his complaint to the court for in camera review within ten days. O'Connor, C.J., dissents.
